[Can Skip All Scenes [Saveable]]
author=bungholio
description=When you beat the game and load again, you can press start to skip all scenes. You can&#039;t do that the first game though. With this, you can. It might have a few side effects that mean nothing. I had the maximum amount of deaths at the end of the game, but the game still gave me the best rank for it. Also when you first pick up any item like fruit, normally the game tells you what it is. It skips that too. Codebreaker 7+ required!
patch=1,EE,404B2228,extended,00110001
patch=1,EE,FFFFFFFF,extended,00000000

