[Main Weapon Modifier [Saveable]]
author=bungholio
description=00 - Reflector 1 - Divine Retribution
01 - Reflector 2 - Snarling Beast
02 - Reflector 3 - Infinity Judge
03 - Reflector 4 - Trinity Mirror
04 - Reflector 5 - Solar Flare
10 - Glave 1 - Tsumugari
11 - Glave 2 - Seven Strike
12 - Glave 3 - Blade of Kusanagi
13 - Glave 4 - Eighth Wonder
14 - Glave 5 - Thunder Edge
20 - Rosary 1 - Devout Beads
21 - Rosary 2 - Life Beads
22 - Rosary 3 - Exorcism Beads
23 - Rosary 4 - Resurrection Beads
24 - Rosary 5 - Tundra Beads

You can have the same weapon equipped to both slots. You don&#039;t need to actually have the weapon either.
patch=1,EE,00683288,extended,00000000

