[Skip Final Boss Fight [Saveable]]
author=bungholio
description=c0 = stage 1 skipped (stage 1 = he floats around and you start without a weapon)
a0 = s1 + s2 skipped (stage 2 = he floats around on fire)
90 = s1 + s2 + s3 skipped (stage 3 = the slot machine thing)
88 = s1 + s2 + s3 + s4 skipped (stage 4 = he has arms and legs, lightning in the sky)
fe = skip the whole boss and end the game quickly
patch=1,EE,004ADA07,extended,000000C0

[Skip The Speech Before Final Boss Fight [Saveable]]
author=bungholio
description=Normally that merchant guy stops you when you step into the light and yaps away for about 15 seconds. Skip him.
patch=1,EE,004AD8DC,extended,00000020

